(\cos(\theta) - i\sin(\theta)) = \sqrt[n]{\cos(n\theta) - i\sin(n\theta)} = \sqrt[n]{\cos(n\theta) - \sqrt{-\sin^2(n\theta)}}
= \sqrt[n]{\cos(n\theta) - \sqrt{-(1-\cos^2(n\theta))}} = \sqrt[n]{\cos(n\theta) -\sqrt{\cos^2(n\theta) - 1}}
